Text: OnePass Offers Spend and Earn Bonus Milesweekend Plans Dont worry weve got you covered Low lastminute fares are available every week to help you visit family friends and many great destinations around the country COOL Travel Specials are a great way to burn those extra OnePass miles Dont miss out on any more opportunities Register today with your OnePass number for COOL Travel Specials email and get ready for your next trip Earn Bonus miles every night Theres Still Time As a Continental OnePass member when you register for MilesByNightSM you earn bonus miles every night you stay at participating hotels during March and April in addition to the bonus miles you usually earn per stay The MilesByNight bonus is available at more than participating Westin Hotels Resortsc Sheraton Hotels Resortsc St Regisc The Luxury Collectionc and W Hotelsc in the US Big Apple Bonus When you stay at any of our nine New York City Manhattan hotels youll receive bonus miles instead of Theres no limit to the bonus miles you can earn during this promotion You must register for MilesByNight to earn OnePass bonus miles Just click the link below for more information and to register Start earning tonight mbnmmcomalemco Terms and Conditions UNFORTUNATELY MAIL SENT TO THIS ADDRESS CANNOT BE ANSWERED PLEASE DIRECT ALL INQUIRIES TO OAIRCOM Note To modify your OnePass email preferences please login to Your Account at wwwonepasscomyouraccount To unsubscribe from all OnePass partner email programs please visit wwwonepasscomemailpartoffers IMAGE
